{"word":"λαιμός 1","slug":"λαιμός 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n61660\" key=\"laimo/s1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">λαιμός</orth> (A), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, <sense id=\"n61660.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">throat, gullet</tr_>, in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> always of men, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">βάλε δουρὶ λαιμὸν ὑπ᾽ ἀνθερεῶνα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:388\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.388</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸν δ᾽ Ὀδυσεὺς κατὰ λαιμὸν . . βάλεν ἰῷ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.15</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὔ πως ἂν ἔμοιγε φίλον κατὰ λαιμὸν ἰείη οὐ πόσις οὐδὲ βρῶσις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:209\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.209</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λ. ἀπαμήσειε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.34</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: metaph., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">neck</tr_> of a bottle, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"ti